      "content": "thanks. one more thing, we're also looking at how this affects the surface quality. some clients are asking for a very tight, impenetrable-feeling finish so nothing can penetrate the surface easily during use. if we reach a certain threshold of density, is there a point where the weave acts more like a physical barrier than just a fabric?",
